Cyberpunk style: A glowing holographic coffee bean floating in a neon-lit void, with luminous data streams and circuit patterns flowing into and out of it like synapses. The bean is semi-transparent, revealing an intricate internal network of interconnected nodes and pathways in electric blue and hot pink. Thin, elegant tendrils of light extend from the bean, each connecting to small floating geometric UI elements - toggles, sliders, and dials that pulse with energy. The background is a deep purple-black gradient with subtle grid lines fading into the distance. The overall mood is technical yet organic, suggesting the seamless binding between a simple object and complex systems. Rain droplets catch the neon reflections in the foreground, adding depth and atmosphere.
